1. Gioi thieu nhanh ve salesforce
Provides ways to collaborate with people you work with.

And it does all those things.
va no lam tat ca nhung dieu do

Khong the noi salesforce chi la CRM (just a CRM)

There's a lot more to it than that
Con nhieu dieu hon the nua
Salesforce comes with a lot of standard functionality
salesforce di kem voi rart nhieu chuc nang tieu chuan

that you can use to run your business.
ma ban co the su dung de dieu hoanh doanh nghiep

Here are some common things businesses want to do with Salesforce
O day co 1 vai thu pho bien ma cac doanh nghiep muon lam voi salesforce

Work on the go
Lam viec tren duong di

Collaborate with coworkers, partners, and customers
Phoi hop voi dong nghiep, doi tac, va khach hang (Slack, Chatter and Communities to connect your cp)

Market to your audience
Tiep thi cho khan gia cua ban (Marketing Cloud to manage your customer journeys)

Object is one of many important terms you'll learn as you get to know Salesforce.
Object la mot trong nhieu thuat ngu quan trong  ma ban se hoc khi ban tiep xuc voi salesforce


